author: Natalia Lusinski
title: This “Pretty Little Liars” actor just welcomed a baby, and we’re so happy for him
text:
This “Pretty Little Liars” actor just welcomed a baby, and we’re so happy for him Yes, the news is true — this Pretty Little Liars actor just welcomed a baby , reported People , and we’re so happy for him. The actor? Nicholas Gonzalez. He and his wife, Kelsey, just had a baby girl , Ever Lee Wilde Gonzalez, on March 1st in Los Angeles. On Facebook, Nicholas said it was the “best day of our life.” We bet!
“We are looking forward to sleepless nights and blissed-out days,” Nicholas and Kelsey told People. “We are so in love with our new, little person. She is the best thing — ever!” Let’s see this baby already, right?! Ever Lee Wilde Gonzalez 3-1-17 8lbs 1oz 21in. "Your children are not your children. They are the sons and daughters of life's longing for itself." #everleewilde 
A post shared by nicholas gonzalez (@eltexmex) on Mar 2, 2017 at 7:52pm PST 
A . And don’t you love the Kahlil Gibran quote, too?! Nice touch! A few months ago, Nicholas even posted this on IG, so you can compare and contrast with the above pic.
'76 Vs. '83 Wonder which one the little one will favor... 
A post shared by nicholas gonzalez (@eltexmex) on Dec 22, 2016 at 4:54pm PST 
Fun-ny! Any thoughts?! Overall, Nicholas seemed excited about having the baby.
#wcw There may even be a 2 for 1 situation here... Happy 30 weeks, Lover! I am so proud of you and in awe of your strength. 
A post shared by nicholas gonzalez (@eltexmex) on Dec 14, 2016 at 1:38pm PST 
She's a natural @joellehorowitz. #TopGolf #Vegas #GolfingForTwo #PregnantGolf

And Nicholas and Kelsey seem ~super happy~ together. imagine me and you. i do. #aintnobody 
A post shared by nicholas gonzalez (@eltexmex) on Feb 14, 2017 at 5:27pm PST 
To the life of the party and the light of my life...#wcw : @melissacoulier 
A post shared by nicholas gonzalez (@eltexmex) on Dec 7, 2016 at 12:15pm PST 
Okay, is anyone else having #relationshipgoals rn, or is it just us?! ICYMI, the couple got married in April of 2016, and they seem like the perfect couple.
As far as their new baby goes, we doubt she’ll slow Nicholas and Kelsey down. He continues to act, of course, and has been in everything from the aforementioned PLL to How to Get Away with Murder. He’ll be in the third season of Narcos , too. Kelsey works as a producer and actress, starring in shows such as PLL and Scandal . In addition, she owns QuenchStaffing.com, a staffing agency.
We congratulate the couple on their new baby and hope they don’t have too many of those sleepless nights Nicholas mentioned!
